               <p>By the mid <date>1750s</date> Clarke was widowed and had a small house in
                     <placeName>Christopher&apos;s Alley</placeName> (now <placeName>Christopher
                     Street</placeName>), <placeName>Moorfields</placeName>, where &apos;a few of
